scripts.text: You enter the great kitchens of the castle. Huge pots simmer over red coals, and the smell of freshly baked bread comes from giant ovens. Cooks and servants bustle this way that, ignoring you.
You enter the armoury. Great store of fine swords and spears and other arms line the walls and are heaped on the floors.

Access To The 
Gate Is Restricted
This chamber is a spartan temple dedicated to the worship of the goddess The Lady.
